features: (3 Pack) Exo Terra Terrarium Cover Clip Set, Large, 2 Clips each
Help keep aquarium and glass tank screen covers secure
These clips are specifically designed for use with Exo Terra Aquarium Screen Covers, both hinged and unhinged
Since aquariums, tanks, and terrariums vary in size, the shape of our Screen Cover Clips can be tightened or loosened by applying gentle pressure
description: Keep your reptile’s enclosure even more secure with a set of Exo Terra’s Terrarium Screen Cover Clip Set. These heavy-duty plastic clips can be attached to Exo Terrarium screen covers to make sure your pet stays safely inside. They’re easy to install in seconds, and they help provide peace of mind for pet parents with no need to worry about their pets escaping!
